        "content": "### Read Pending Queue (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Keep Valid Leads · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT",
